## âœ… When to Use What?

- Use **Ansible** when you prioritize deeper configuration granularity, workflow orchestration, compliance enforcement, and cross-domain automation.
- Use **Terraform** if your team prefers declarative, state-managed infrastructure-as-code workflowsâ€”especially if you're already using Terraform for cloud automation and want to unify your toolchain.

